; Regression test for issue #864: 'ledger -YBj reg' no longer works with multiple commodities
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/864
;
; The -YBj reg command (yearly cost-basis gnuplot output) should work with
; multiple commodities, converting them all to cost basis before summing.
; Previously this errored: "Cannot convert a balance with multiple commodities
; to an amount"

2020/03/01 Buy AAPL
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL @ $100.00
    Assets:Cash

2020/06/01 Buy EUR
    Assets:Bank    500 EUR @ $1.10
    Assets:Cash

test -YBj reg Assets:Brokerage
2020-01-01 1000
end test

test -YBj reg Assets:Bank
2020-01-01 550
end test

test -YBj reg
2020-01-01 550
2020-01-01 1000
2020-01-01 -1550
end test
